Class TapjoyFeaturedAppObject

java.lang.Object
  com.tapjoy.TapjoyFeaturedAppObject

public class TapjoyFeaturedAppObject
extends java.lang.Object

The TapjoyFeaturedAppObject represents a full screen ad object and is initialized when the server responds to the URL request for getting the feature app data is completed.
